sql: SELECT Allergy_Type.Allergy FROM Allergy_Type JOIN Allergy_Type AS i ON Allergy_Type.Allergy = i.Allergy LIMIT 2

SELECT COUNT(StuID), COUNT(DISTINCT AllergyType), AllergyType FROM Allergy_Type JOIN Has_Allergy ON Has_Allergy.Allergy = Allergy_Type.Allergy WHERE  StuID >= 18 GROUP BY AllergyType HAVING COUNT(StuID) > 34
SELECT Has_Allergy.Allergy, f.Allergy FROM Has_Allergy AS f JOIN Has_Allergy ON Has_Allergy.StuID = f.StuID WHERE  f.StuID <= 100 GROUP BY f.Allergy ORDER BY Has_Allergy.Allergy DESC LIMIT 7
SELECT v.Major, v.Age FROM Student AS v WHERE  v.StuID != 6 ORDER BY v.Major DESC

SELECT AVG(Has_Allergy.StuID), MAX(Major), COUNT(DISTINCT Has_Allergy.Allergy) FROM Student JOIN Allergy_Type JOIN Has_Allergy ON Has_Allergy.Allergy = Allergy_Type.Allergy AND Student.StuID = Has_Allergy.StuID WHERE  Age = 44
SELECT AVG(StuID), StuID, Allergy FROM Has_Allergy WHERE  StuID = 77 GROUP BY Allergy ORDER BY StuID DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT f.LName FROM Student AS f WHERE  f.Advisor <= 85
SELECT AllergyType FROM Allergy_Type ORDER BY AllergyType DESC
SELECT StuID, StuID, Has_Allergy.Allergy FROM Allergy_Type JOIN Has_Allergy ON Has_Allergy.Allergy = Allergy_Type.Allergy GROUP BY Has_Allergy.Allergy HAVING MIN(StuID) < 93

SELECT AVG(StuID), COUNT(DISTINCT StuID), AllergyType FROM Allergy_Type JOIN Has_Allergy ON Has_Allergy.Allergy = Allergy_Type.Allergy WHERE  StuID >= 13 GROUP BY AllergyType ORDER BY AllergyType ASC LIMIT 3
SELECT x.StuID, x.StuID, x.Allergy FROM Has_Allergy AS x WHERE  x.StuID != 84 LIMIT 10
SELECT MAX(StuID), COUNT(DISTINCT StuID), COUNT(DISTINCT StuID), Allergy FROM Has_Allergy WHERE  StuID <= 0 GROUP BY Allergy HAVING COUNT(StuID) >= 43
SELECT StuID, StuID, Allergy FROM Has_Allergy WHERE  StuID <= 29 OR StuID NOT IN (SELECT StuID FROM Student AS s WHERE  s.Age < 94) GROUP BY Allergy HAVING SUM(StuID) < 26 LIMIT 6
SELECT COUNT(StuID), StuID, StuID FROM Allergy_Type JOIN Has_Allergy ON Has_Allergy.Allergy = Allergy_Type.Allergy WHERE  StuID != 94
SELECT StuID FROM Has_Allergy WHERE  StuID >= 21
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT StuID), Major FROM Student LIMIT 4
SELECT Sex FROM Student JOIN Has_Allergy ON Student.StuID = Has_Allergy.StuID WHERE  Advisor > 1 ORDER BY Sex ASC
SELECT StuID, StuID, Allergy FROM Has_Allergy WHERE StuID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  StuID <= 24 GROUP BY Allergy HAVING SUM(StuID) > 96 ORDER BY StuID DESC LIMIT 6
